n Monte Carlo\ntechniques are circumvented which allows the use of pseudo and quasi-random\nnumbers. In the latter case better convergence rates can be observed both in\nthe linear and nonlinear phase.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Jun 2020 18:56:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-26"}
