 some POIs (e.g., Restaurant and Other Eating Places)\nremained stable during the social distancing period, while some POIs had an\nincreased proportion of visits (e.g., Grocery Stores). The findings highlight\nthat social distancing orders do yield disparate patterns of reduction in\nmovements to hotspots POIs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Jun 2020 03:54:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Jun 2020 03:01:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-29"}
