ysis on the evaluation of FWH acoustic signals utilizing reduced fluid\ndynamic fields as input demonstrates that both DMD and PODI data-driven reduced\nmodels are efficient and sufficiently accurate in predicting acoustic noises.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Jun 2020 14:06:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 Dec 2020 10:07:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-29"}
