wer is also extracted, revealing interesting physical\ninsights about the 2D layered GO films. Finally, we obtain an enhancement in\nthe effective nonlinear parameter of the hybrid waveguides by over a factor of\n100. These results verify the enhanced nonlinear optical performance of SiN\nwaveguides achievable by incorporating 2D layered GO films.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Jun 2020 02:13:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-29"}
