ility recovering momentum is further fueled by the Black Lives Matter\nprotests, potentially fostering the second wave of infections in the U.S.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Jun 2020 23:21:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-03"}
